<h1>Bankruptcy Advice</h1>
<h1>Please enter your total financial obligations</h1>
<div style="width: 30%; margin: 25px auto;">
<form action="/bankruptcy" method="POST">
<div class="form-group">
<h3>Income</h3>
<label for="expense">What is your yearly income(after taxes): </label>
<input type="number" name="housingBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense" /><br/>
 <label for="expense">Outstanding tax obligation amount: </label></br>
<input type="number" name="taxBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense-Amount" /><br>
</div>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<h3>Housing</h3>
<label for="expense">Monthly mortage: </label></br>
<input type="number" name="mortageBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense" /><br/>
 <label for="expense">Rent Obligation (amount * number of months): </label></br>
<input type="number" name="rentBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense-Amount" /><br>
<label for="expense">I own a home (Appraisal rate for house): </label></br>
<input type="number" name="homeBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense-Amount" /><br>
<br>
<br>
<h3>Transporation</h3>
<label for="expense">Car payment: </label></br>
<input type="number" name="carBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense" /><br/>
<br>
<br>
<h3>Health</h3>
<label for="expense">Do you have health insurance (Yes or No): </label>
<input type="text" name="insuranceBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense" /><br/>
 <label for="expense">Outstanding medical bills: </label></br>
<input type="number" name="medicalBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense-Amount" /><br>
<br>
<br>
<h3>Legal</h3>
<label for="expense">Do you have any pending legal cases: </label>
<input type="text" name="legalBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense" /><br/>
 <label for="expense">Do you have any pending legal settlement against you (Child support, car accident, speeding tickets): </label></br>
<input type="number" name="pendingBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense-Amount" /><br>
<label for="expense">Do you have pending legal fees: </label>
 <input type="number" name="pendingLegalBankruptcy" placeholder="category" /><br/>
<br>
<br>
<h3>Savings</h3>
<label for="expense">Total amount in checkings account: </label>
<input type="number" name="savingBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense" /><br/>
 <label for="expense">Total amount in savings account: </label>
<input type="number" name="totalSavingBankruptcy" placeholder="Expense-Amount" /><br>
</div>
 <a class="button is-success" href="/budget">Back</a><br>
   <input type="submit" value="Submit">
 </form>
